{"type":"message","id":"40d842d6","parentId":"2932c423","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:00:10.394Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bzG9i4I8lpoDJqCOFMtgeqgs|fc_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8091b260c81919a329c8cd99166d5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\notion-integration-notes.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":320,"aggregated":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\notion-integration-notes.md","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774717210392}}
{"type":"message","id":"20979fbd","parentId":"40d842d6","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:00:12.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_KsCFDROvROvmeDApah57eCsq|fc_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8091d2bd481919c21a33303ac1e4d","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace\\notion-integration-notes.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\notion-integration-notes.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":133,"output":38,"cacheRead":9216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9387,"cost":{"input":0.0003325,"output":0.00057,"cacheRead":0.002304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032065}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774717210394,"responseId":"resp_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8091c60248191b084fd7d53439f8a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d593ee5","parentId":"20979fbd","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:00:12.309Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_KsCFDROvROvmeDApah57eCsq|fc_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8091d2bd481919c21a33303ac1e4d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Notion integration notes\n\n## Estado\n\nSí hay integración usable con Notion en esta máquina.\n\n## Método\n\nUsar la API oficial de Notion con token disponible en variable de entorno local:\n\n- `NOTION_TOKEN`\n\nCabeceras base:\n\n```powershell\n$headers = @{\n  'Authorization' = \"Bearer $env:NOTION_TOKEN\"\n  'Notion-Version' = '2025-09-03'\n  'Content-Type' = 'application/json'\n}\n```\n\n## Operaciones base\n\n### Buscar páginas\n\n```powershell\nInvoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri 'https://api.notion.com/v1/search' -Headers $headers -Body '{\"query\":\"Atlas OS\"}'\n```\n\n### Leer bloques hijos\n\n```powershell\nInvoke-RestMethod -Method Get -Uri 'https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/<block_or_page_id>/children?page_size=100' -Headers $headers\n```\n\n### Añadir bloques\n\n```powershell\nInvoke-RestMethod -Method Patch -Uri 'https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/<block_or_page_id>/children' -Headers $headers -Body $bodyJson\n```\n\n### Archivar bloque\n\n```powershell\nInvoke-RestMethod -Method Patch -Uri 'https://api.notion.com/v1/blocks/<block_id>' -Headers $headers -Body '{\"archived\":true}'\n```\n\n## Página principal\n\n- Nombre: `Atlas OS`\n- Uso: tablero operativo visual / seguimiento de tareas\n\n## Nota operativa\n\nLa API puede dar problemas de encoding con emojis/símbolos en algunos flujos de PowerShell. Preferir texto limpio/ASCII cuando algo visual se rompa.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774717212307}}
{"type":"message","id":"9cff00eb","parentId":"7d593ee5","timestamp":"2026-03-28T17:00:19.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Querying task database**\n\nI need to read all tasks from the database using its ID. First, I should perform a query to gather that data. I might determine the schema properties as I go along. To handle this, I plan to use exec alongside a PowerShell script that will output the JSON in a simplified format. This should streamline my process and make it easier to extract the information I need.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c80920061c8191972cee5a744c76ea\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpyAkkAZCxUpz97jlQdZ1NgHo3kXB8q6L-wRTX6IPWwoKcz8C5fGFNPXID3ha483mtVBhVOs5symDYu9LTIvNRwWrcDVWncn6483M37FtegKEeJhxH3ZupOVEziMZJ-XqMxeBNQyejTkl4Gbs0nUeMPCW0T2EprKSzs93xlACrsaAS2ueBaYg7Odct-x5iYsbaTKJNMFNucsQwBqIxk0Qfp1wrWf7bZ3WibE_b4hpd20Sa2hnUNhO08zCnOAeUsyyxZQdg-_Vlcp8MJU1fe2opeFr5jfQjg2wdRyhmx7lymnYbz_mOCZCf4ZYzm4qUvm_2sU-cc2vwjQw0s2HcFFPEEHieA7NLtdTFla7Lcils2hYWZSsPkqTMbz4P0VGuGs7iifTo_JNiHmDeOemGr2G4OG2-Bl3r9E4fSeuplWXkWLbF3R4j7vKwU3Wf7W1zoNCJoaa9ffIXlhUgIXZtwtZb5OZ4WqGNDdg2tM2E-7AygHB--hX6Y-goCMhRp-242q3TQdBsgCxRgiQc4j4CwedXAiDFAKuCYICuFQC9sGsYa3TomCzxKMbIIdKyXQ8SZkR60FOqwPMgs3PEcBdb1xSoAIMDlqGLMdg5vZ0w_c964X6HhZugYjjkpDWnJpV1Zg-XngBVAQISFaiAEmnCfqPrtUGnniLRHS0V6q5g2hjXkxFqq5cJYF0UOsZqTQxN657syhsWuwtOh9nrNES8n9Ngtlv4r9e8UabaJzl_aw1UhB_3zdb5bXuAvrTD7S3_X-BkYU2omsaRe4zYCeQTjs6tfB1URXOEYXB_jSxGdSiHTMqDf18Hi4cpk0B-_b-zRUACK5FyVb8U-l7r85fnowl7zQF_3uagJDGVW8WENQ5b0Z-BoXz3bHuX0mKAlGsOEDmIgeqIFyA-C5c6oegHRCvIPRwb0uwEP_MbQv3ergtSVtOTelw0Kd0fMRfSrlhrne13GmtEOpdRNVRsHlp8O42iU1JXlHzKNu76vL3znWqo2x7QZKLsf5nUPEKta1IdFMIOb1Wy\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Querying task database**\\n\\nI need to read all tasks from the database using its ID. First, I should perform a query to gather that data. I might determine the schema properties as I go along. To handle this, I plan to use exec alongside a PowerShell script that will output the JSON in a simplified format. This should streamline my process and make it easier to extract the information I need.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Voy a leer el tracker de Notion, coordinar a los agentes responsables y luego dejar el estado reflejado antes del resumen.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c809243f4481918e5829f24926a45f\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YZW0o1UDuerUAgjWi2ni3brs|fc_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8092475288191a5004e9b9c762d46","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$ErrorActionPreference='Stop'\n$headers = @{ 'Authorization' = \"Bearer $env:NOTION_TOKEN\"; 'Notion-Version' = '2025-09-03'; 'Content-Type' = 'application/json' }\n$body = '{\"page_size\":100}'\n$r = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri 'https://api.notion.com/v1/data_sources/32f0a0b1-97cc-81a8-9443-df3f85f2ffc7/query' -Headers $headers -Body $body\n$r | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 100","workdir":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"$ErrorActionPreference='Stop'\\n$headers = @{ 'Authorization' = \\\"Bearer $env:NOTION_TOKEN\\\"; 'Notion-Version' = '2025-09-03'; 'Content-Type' = 'application/json' }\\n$body = '{\\\"page_size\\\":100}'\\n$r = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri 'https://api.notion.com/v1/data_sources/32f0a0b1-97cc-81a8-9443-df3f85f2ffc7/query' -Headers $headers -Body $body\\n$r | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 100\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":535,"output":243,"cacheRead":9216,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9994,"cost":{"input":0.0013375000000000001,"output":0.0036450000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002304,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007286500000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774717212310,"responseId":"resp_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8091f69