Atlas OS review - midday","updatedAt":1774717201043,"sessionId":"787b6e38-4264-461a-9643-fc5618ef10cd","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":57136,"estimatedCostUsd":1.2783175,"status":"running","startedAt":1774717201009,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\787b6e38-4264-461a-9643-fc5618ef10cd.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Coordinating tasks and ownership**\n\nI need to ensure each Backlog or Next task has a clear owner. It seems that currently, only the Backlog has no assigned owner, and there are no Next tasks. The instructions suggest I should actively coordinate the owners for each task. Perhaps it would be helpful to address any blocked or ambiguous tasks. I might also consider coordinating with Ares or Hestia on these blocked tasks, and I should identify sessions for agents using the sessions_list."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a6Chu2POdFIlRuxrtymk53ZG|fc_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c8094c6be881919ce0a113648b625a","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":50,"messageLimit":1},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":50,\"messageLimit\":1}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2673,"output":116,"totalTokens":43237,"cacheRead":40448,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.018534500000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774717249801,"responseId":"resp_012e12a4adaf4cd90169c80943e2e48191a6f2c3d322b7a950","__openclaw":{"id":"648fb8d2","seq":18}}]},{"key":"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+573183718246","kind":"other","channel":"whatsapp","displayName":"+573183718246","deliveryContext":{"channel":"whatsapp","to":"+573183718246","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1774717048701,"sessionId":"0d303feb-efbe-466c-98c4-f85e7ae2c721","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":43009,"estimatedCostUsd":0.3782935,"status":"done","startedAt":1774717023145,"endedAt":1774717048650,"runtimeMs":25505,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"whatsapp","lastTo":"+573183718246","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\0d303feb-efbe-466c-98c4-f85e7ae2c721.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" Perfecto. Ya me queda la regla:\n\n- **Vercel/GitHub de ese tipo** → marcarlos como leído **por defecto**\n- **ZooLATECH** → dejarlo fuera de seguimiento y también marcarlo leído si aparece\n- **excepto** si veo un mensaje realmente distinto/importante\n\nY ahora mismo, en la validación rápida:\n- **no me aparecieron ya como unread**\n- tampoco apareció **ZooLATECH** como no leído\n\nO sea, **ya no están pendientes en unread** o cambiaron de estado.\n\n**Regla que adopto desde ahora:**\ncuando en las revisiones vea:\n- ruido repetitivo de **Vercel/GitHub** sobre lo mismo,\n- o vuelva a aparecer **ZooLATECH** como si fuera pendiente viejo,\n\nlo trataré como:\n- **no prioritario**\n- **sin repetírtelo**\n- y con intención de **limpiarlo** si hace falta\n\nSi quieres, el siguiente paso bueno es que yo **actualice esa preferencia en memoria** para no volver a caer en lo mismo en futuras sesiones.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_08605887b83f1aa90169c80875ab4881918ac601cb1859144e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":129,"output":239,"totalTokens":43248,"cacheRead":42880,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.014627500000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774717042395,"responseId":"resp_08605887b83f1aa90169c808747d0c8191a2559b0426d55eed","__openclaw":{"id":"348742cf","seq":54}}]},{"key":"agent:ares:whatsapp:group:120363424964463765@g.us","kind":"group","channel":"whatsapp","displayName":"whatsapp:g-smart-project","deliveryContext":{"channel":"whatsapp","to":"120363424964463765@g.us","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1774716870699,"sessionId":"ab39ca96-3156-4ab5-b3ea-01d9077ab56d","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":29765,"estimatedCostUsd":0.366941,"status":"running","startedAt":1774716361309,"endedAt":1774716410227,"runtimeMs":6708,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"whatsapp","lastTo":"120363424964463765@g.us","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\ares\\sessions\\ab39ca96-3156-4ab5-b3ea-01d9077ab56d.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Determining response necessity**\n\nIt seems like the user might have sent a message to confirm something. I need to figure out if they want an answer for the current session or if it’s something from a previous interaction. They probably want a real-time status update. If that’s the case, I can let them know “ejecutado en canal externo,” as this might indicate the delivery was successful. I want to make sure I get this right for them!"},{"type":"text","text":" ejecutado en canal externo.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0821345abba5ec180169c805fb83248191becbecb8b13ccea9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":29765,"output":65,"totalTokens":29830,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.07538750000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774716403526,"responseId":"resp_0821345abba5ec180169c805f57e1c8191b5a721bd5b7e93f6","__openclaw":{"id":"b3909cea","seq":139}}]},{"key":"agent:main:tui-104fc32a-4543-4770-a2ca-02f8fde7383b","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774716570036,"sessionId":"792032df-f362-4870-ab66-658780af0351","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"estimatedCostUsd":0.003168,"status":"done","startedAt":1774363124606,"endedAt":1774363129589,"runtimeMs":4983,"childSessions":["agent:main:subagent:9dc03af6-f7ea-43a5-b470-4a2a2b60927e"],"systemSent":false,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPa